$interpreted: Soohyeon: A leopard!
Law: That's right. One of the last remaining leopards, forced out of his own land by Sennosuke himself.
Law: The Alliance itself wasn't doing anything to help him, so I had to put matters into my own hands.
Jia-Shen: Don't worry, Master Law's here! Tell him everything you know!
Yota: My name is Yota... I'm Himawari's twin brother...
Yota: Back then, when we were both still young... this tyrant...
Yota: He deceived our mother, Mitsuru, into owing him a huge debt. In the end, we could only pay him back with our ancestor's land...
Sennosuke: Mitsuru? Doesn't ring a bell...
Law: Silence! Let Yota continue!
Yota: ...Taking our land is one thing, but then... but then he forced my mother to... to transfer her power to him.
Yota: My mother agreed, but in secret she planned to kill him the second the chance arose.
Yota: In the end, my sister and I could do nothing but hide in the kitchen cupboard while he... while he...
Jia-Shen: You were just a kid back then... You can't blame yerself.
Yota: ...Finally, while my sister and I were escaping, we got split up... He caught me, but I don't know where my sister ended up...
Miranda: (...Himawari, is this why you hated your own power? It couldn't protect your mother, it only got her killed...)
Yota: Since then, Sennosuke has tortured me... forced me into transferring my own power to this woman...
Himawari: ......
Yota: I couldn't help but give some of that power over, through years of torture... but to keep myself alive, I've retained some of it.
Yota: They know there's still some left. I still have value... and that's why they've kept me alive.
Yota: If Law didn't find me, then I... I...
Maeok: ......
Panther Chieftain: ......
Toyokuni: ......
Law: So. You have your proof. Far off from his claims of 'unpaid debts'...
Law: Sennosuke is guilty of Mitsuru's murder, and the transfer of Yota's power! Serious crimes! Will the Alliance truly continue to do nothing!?
Tortoise Chieftain: Now, hold on there little Law. Let me help ol' Sennosuke explain himself...
Sennosuke: There's no need.
Sennosuke: Really, Law? Listen, I applaud this whole performance, really well done. But... a little pathetic, don't you think?
Law: Excuse me? The evidence is clear as day, and you still deny it!?
Sennosuke: Pullin' this leopard punk out of nowhere doesn't prove anything 'cept for the fact that the leopards aren't all dead!
Sennosuke: But are we supposed to take his word for it just cause he's got a frown on his face and a tear in his eye? You could frame the whole Alliance that way!
Sennosuke: Please, everyone, I know you're smart enough not to be duped by this little dog and pony show.
Panther Chieftain: That's right! Since when has it been good practice to prosecute with only one side of the story!?
Law: But...!
Jia-Shen: ......
Yota: I... I have proof...
Yota: To transfer power, both people have to remove their clothing... That night, I saw his body... I saw a mark...
Yota: The place it was in, I wouldn't be surprised if he doesn't even know about it himself. So if I'm right, then that has to be enough proof!
Sennosuke: ......
Law: Yota, write down the location and appearance of the mark. Then we'll have Sennosuke remove his clothes to confirm it.
Law: If you're innocent, Sennosuke, then I'm sure you wouldn't mind cooperating with us.
Sennosuke: ......
Law: It's fine. If you're not willing to do it yourself, we can have someone do it for you.
Maeok: Sennosuke, we're not trying to falsely accuse anyone here. But this is a very big deal. I can only ask that you please cooperate.
Sennosuke: So is that what you all want? Want me to throw myself on the fire?
Sennosuke: Hmph... You need me until you don't, is that it? Now I'm more trouble than I'm worth!?
Maeok: Someone come and remove Sennosuke's robes!
Sennosuke: Get your hands off me!
Law: Finally showing your true colors, hmm?
Maeok: Someone hold him still!
Sennosuke: Have you all forgotten how I've built my empire!? You think I'd let some common rats chew it all down!? Hah!
Law: Someone muzzle this mutt!
Law: I'm here to see justice served, so you can forget about running away!
Sennosuke: Run!? Please, we're not cut from the same cloth, Law. I think bigger than that.
Panther Chieftain: W-W-What are you doing!?
Sennosuke: You're all parasites, all of you! Dogs, begging for scraps! And now you're all gonna repay me with your lives!
Maeok: Let go!
Sennosuke: Eh!? Who the...!?
???: That is my home of love; if I have ranged...
Yan-Bo: Like him that travels... I return again.
Maeok: ...You... you're...!
Law: Hah! You've finally made up your mind, old man!
Yan-Bo: Injustice begets injustice... I see injustice, and come to cleanse it at the source.
Sennosuke: It's you! Yan-Bo!
Sennosuke: Murderer!
Sennosuke: I've been waiting for the moment I could kill you, and avenge Master Kaito!
Juan-Yun: Whew... I'm here, I'm here! Sorry... I'm a little slow!
Pang: Don't apologize! We're both strangers here. If it weren't for you, little lord, we'd be completely in the dark!
Tindoiimu: I wonder how it's going in there?
Sennosuke: I will end you!
Pang: Master Yan-Bo!?
Sennosuke: You're going to die!
Yan-Bo: ...Yah!
Sennosuke: Guhh!!
Yan-Bo: Do not struggle. I've sealed your Qi, if you...
Sennosuke: Gyaaaaaaahhh-!!!
Pang: Did he... shatter his own meridian!?
Yan-Bo: ...Barbaric... just like your master.
Sennosuke: You don't deserve to utter his name!
Sennosuke: I'll kill you! Die!!
Sennosuke: Gyaahh!
Yan-Bo: ...This time I've sealed your lifeline. If you destroy that...
Yan-Bo: You'll die.
Sennosuke: Bwahaha! And so what!? What's a life worth!?
Sennosuke: Stop pretending like you care! I murdered your entire tribe! Come on, get your revenge!
Tindoiimu: (His entire tribe... unforgivable. He deserves to get his revenge...)
Sennosuke: Come on! Do it! Kill me!
Sennosuke: Or are you really just some miserable old coward!?
Law: Today I will act on behalf of fate itself, and end the life of this—
Yan-Bo: —Old friend.
Yan-Bo: Ah...
Tindoiimu: (Yan-Bo's going to kill him...!)
Yan-Bo: ...Child, all those things you've been holding within yourself, I let go of long ago.
Yan-Bo: All that weight... If you insist on keeping it, it'll be your burden alone.
Tindoiimu: (What...)

Yan-Bo: The worth of that, is that which it contains, 
And that is this, and this with thee remains~
Sennosuke: ......
Sennosuke: Who do you think you are...
Sennosuke: Who the hell do you think you are!?
Sennosuke: Get back here! Get back here right now!!
Tindoiimu: ......
Maeok: ....You're back.
Yan-Bo: And so I am.
Pang: Master Yan-Bo... all of this...
Yan-Bo: Please, let us have a drink first. Then we can talk~
